1. Are you going to the restaurant in the evening or not? 2. She is going to
London next week. 3. They are going to buy a new TV set. 4. How do you feel? Are
you going to school tomorrow? 5. Our mother will come soon. 6. She is having lunch
at the Petrovs' tomorrow in the evening. 7. I am leaving for Copenhagen in two days.
8. Your wife will call in the morning. 9. I am meeting with the representative of the
firm tomorrow at ten. 10. They are not going to Riga on Monday. 11. My brother
is getting married in September. 12. I am going to the shop.
